      <title>特朗普竞选团队称遭黑客攻击，并称伊朗应为罪魁祸首</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普的竞选团队表示，其通讯遭到黑客攻击，并暗示伊朗应对此负责，称此举意在干预 11 月的总统大选，特朗普将在大选中与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯对决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-campaign-says-it-was-hacked-suggests-iran-to-blame</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 19:51:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约时报-锡耶纳民意调查显示哈里斯在三个摇摆州领先特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/harris-leads-trump-in-three-key-states-in-nyt-siena-college-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《纽约时报》和锡耶纳学院的一项调查显示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在美国三个战场州的潜在选民中分别领先共和党对手唐纳德·特朗普 4 个百分点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/harris-leads-trump-in-three-key-states-in-nyt-siena-college-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 11:03:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾称中国空军采取危险行动，使用照明弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-says-china-air-force-did-dangerous-move-used-flares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾军方表示，中国空军本周早些时候在南海上空采取了“危险和挑衅行动”，此举可能威胁双方缓解海上紧张局势的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/philippines-says-china-air-force-did-dangerous-move-used-flares</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 10:56:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国对学校学费征收新税，引发对财务建议的需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/new-tax-on-uk-school-fees-prompts-demand-for-financial-advice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于某些英国家长来说，随着暑假的临近和新学年的临近，又有一件令人担心的事：学费即将上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/new-tax-on-uk-school-fees-prompts-demand-for-financial-advice</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>孟加拉国央行行长、首席大法官在抗议声中辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/bangladesh-central-bank-governor-resigns-amid-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[孟加拉国银行行长阿卜杜勒·鲁夫·塔卢克德和首席大法官奥拜杜尔·哈桑辞职，在谢赫·哈西娜政府被推翻几天后，这加剧了经济和行政动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/bangladesh-central-bank-governor-resigns-amid-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 05:57:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普回避“奇怪”的侮辱，寻求重拾 2024 年叙事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-deflects-weird-insult-seeking-to-regain-2024-narrative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普对民主党的攻击予以回击，后者嘲笑他和他的竞选搭档、俄亥俄州参议员 JD 万斯 (JD Vance) 是“怪人”，并称他的对手是“怪物”，特朗普试图重启这场已经导致他的竞选阵地不断下滑的总统竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/trump-deflects-weird-insult-seeking-to-regain-2024-narrative</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 05:23:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>骚乱暴露英国社会分裂 凯尔·斯塔默仍面临威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/threat-to-keir-starmer-persists-as-riots-expose-uk-social-divisions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两周导致数百人被捕的英国骚乱浪潮似乎已经平息，但对于英国首相基尔·斯塔默的新政府来说，威胁依然存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/threat-to-keir-starmer-persists-as-riots-expose-uk-social-divisions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称袭击了学校内的哈马斯指挥部，引发愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军方称，以色列对加沙市发动的致命袭击遭到国际社会谴责，袭击目标是设在一所学校和相邻清真寺内的哈马斯“指挥和控制中心”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-10/israel-strike-on-gaza-school-kills-100-palestinians-hamas-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:45:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜领导人将洪水灾民转移至首都，拒绝外界援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-10/north-korean-leader-says-thousands-of-flood-victims-will-be-brought-to-capital-for-temporary-care</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首尔，韩国（美联社） — 朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，朝鲜不会寻求外部帮助来恢复该国与中国边境附近地区遭受的洪水灾害，并命令官员将数千名流离失所的居民转移到首都，为他们提供更好的照顾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-10/north-korean-leader-says-thousands-of-flood-victims-will-be-brought-to-capital-for-temporary-care</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 10 Aug 2024 04:01:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯称军队仍在奋力击退乌克兰入侵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/russia-s-lipetsk-evacuates-people-after-drone-attack-on-airfield</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯派遣军事增援部队，与乌克兰军队在俄罗斯西部库尔斯克地区进行对峙，这是自第二次世界大战以来外国首次入侵俄罗斯领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/russia-s-lipetsk-evacuates-people-after-drone-attack-on-airfield</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 04:41:51 GMT</pubDate>
